  <h1>Stay Connected</h1>
  <p class="subscribe-intro">
    Join a community of individuals seeking renewed progress, joy, and purpose in their work and life.
  </p>
  
  <div class="subscribe-benefits">
    <h3>What you'll receive:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Weekly insights on personal development and self-understanding</li>
      <li>Practical strategies for teams and individuals</li>
      <li>Occasional deep dives into technology and creativity</li>
      <li>Early access to new resources and content</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
